4.  frontend/core/credentials.py — Cache directory uses old name
Problem: caches credentials in ~/.clusterpulse. Everything else in beta4.1 uses ~/.cloud_health.
Fix:
Replace :
CACHE_DIR  = Path.home() / ".clusterpulse"
With:
CACHE_DIR  = Path.home() / ".cloud_health"
(Note: Like version_sync.py, this module is currently unused — the bootstrapper inlines its own crypto. But if you import it later, the paths should match.)
